OL,3,CYoung people to have free movement
OL,4,Cacross UK in new European Commission
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FWords by Caleb Tutt
OL,9,FThe (EC) is hoping to start talks with
OL,10,Fthe UK to draw up a post-Brexit deal
OL,11,Fto give young people more
OL,12,Fopportunities to study and work in
OL,13,FEurope.
OL,15,FThe Commission's proposed deal would
OL,16,Fmake it easier for UK citizens aged
OL,17,Fbetween 18 and 30 to work and study in
OL,18,Fthe European Union (EU) and vice versa.
