OL,3,CYoung people to have free movement
OL,4,Cacross UK in new European Commission
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FUnder the current plans, the scheme
OL,8,Fwould allow participants to stay in
OL,9,Ftheir host country for four years.
OL,11,FAlthough the Commission would prefer
OL,12,Fthis deal to be EU-wide, Downing
OL,13,FStreet has said its existing bilateral
OL,14,Fschemes are in the UK's best interest,
OL,15,Fmeaning it is unclear what a final
OL,16,Fdeal would look like.
OL,18,FThe government said it prefers country-
OL,19,Fto-country deals rather than a blanket
OL,20,Frule applying to all 27 EU member
OL,21,Fstates.
