OL,7,FIt said its existing schemes with
OL,8,Findividual EU member states already
OL,9,Fdeliver for students and
OL,10,Fprofessionals, and that it wants to
OL,11,Freduce legal migration and support UK
OL,12,Ftalent.
OL,14,FIn a statement on Thursday, EC Vice
OL,15,FPresident Maros Sefcovic said: "The
OL,16,FUnited Kingdom's withdrawal from the
OL,17,FEuropean Union has hit young people in
OL,18,Fthe EU and the UK who would like to
OL,19,Fstudy, work and live abroad
OL,20,Fparticularly hard.
