OL,7,F"Today, we take the first step towards
OL,8,Fan ambitious but realistic agreement
OL,9,Fbetween the EU and the UK that would
OL,10,Ffix this issue. Our aim is to rebuild
OL,11,Fhuman bridges between young Europeans
OL,12,Fon both sides of the Channel."
OL,14,FChair of the Labour Movement in
OL,15,FEurope, Stella Creasy MP, welcomed the
OL,16,Ftalks and praised the "willingness of
OL,17,Fthe EU to consider a mobility
OL,18,Fagreement".
