OL,7,FMs Creasy said: "Since Brexit, our
OL,8,Fyoung people lost out on jobs,
OL,9,Funiversity places and countless
OL,10,Fopportunities all because they can't
OL,11,Feasily move across Europe.
OL,13,F"Labour must now be clear that, in
OL,14,FGovernment, we will not let this
OL,15,Fopportunity to help limit the damage
OL,16,Fleaving the EU has done to our young
OL,17,Fpeople pass us by."
