OL,7,FThe Commission also said the deal
OL,8,Fshould not include "excessive" visa
OL,9,Ffees and should provide "equal
OL,10,Ftreatment" for those paying
OL,11,Feducational fees and working jobs.
OL,13,FHowever, the deal would not undo the
OL,14,Ffreedoms of movement lost by the UK
OL,15,Fwhen it left the EU, and it would be
OL,16,Fdifferent to the Erasmus+ programme
OL,17,Fwhich allows students to easily study
OL,18,Fabroad.
