OL,7,FThe UK withdrew from the Erasmus+
OL,8,Fprogramme in 2021 due to concerns over
OL,9,Fcosts from former Prime Minister Boris
OL,10,FJohnson, replacing it with the Turing
OL,11,Fscheme which allows opportunities to
OL,12,Fstudy worldwide.
OL,14,FBut, the EC said it's open to talks of
OL,15,Fthe UK rejoining the Erasmus+
OL,16,Fprogramme should it want to.
